Cayce")  Well, here he is, <G>  This file  says; "Bonnie, I'm Egar Cayce"  it 
is obvious that he is in Heaven beyond  the white light, so that is the 
reason for so much static.  This is truly  beginners luck, i am grateful to Mr 
Cayce to speak to us.  I'm sure there  is more on here, but I would say this 
is good enough for  now.sf
